headline: Here's How Many Shares of AT&T You Must Own to Make $5,000 in Annual Dividend Income
summary: You'll need a six-figure amount to buy enough AT&T shares to make $5,000 in annual dividend income.  The number of shares required could change if the telecom giant increases or decreases its dividend payout.  AT&T's dividend appears to be safe right now.
